===Etymology===
From {{affix|en|mill|stone}}, ultimately from {{der|en|gem-pro|*malaną||to [[grind#Verb|grind]]}}, {{m|gem-pro|*muljaną||to [[crush#Verb|crush]] (into pieces), to grind}} (from {{der|en|ine-pro|*melh₂-||to crush, to grind}}, from {{m|ine-pro|*mel-}}) + {{der|en|gem-pro|*stainaz||[[stone]]}} (from {{der|en|ine-pro|*stāi-}}); cognate with {{cog|da|møllesten}}, {{cog|dum|molensteen}} (modern {{cog|nl|molensteen}}), {{cog|fy|molestien}}, {{cog|nb|møllestein}}, {{cog|osx|mulinstēn}} ({{cog|gml|mȫlenstēn}}), {{cog|goh|mulinstein}}, {{m|goh|mülstein}} ({{cog|gmh|mülstein}}, modern {{cog|de|Mühlstein}}).

