===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[large]] [[round]] [[stone]] used for [[grind]]ing [[grain]].
# {{lb|en|geology}} A [[coarse]]-[[grain]]ed [[sandstone]] used for making such stones; [[millstone grit]].
# {{lb|en|figurative}} ''Often in'' '''a millstone round one's neck''' (referring to [[Matthew]] 18:6 in the [[Bible]]): a [[heavy]] [[responsibility]] that is [[difficult]] to [[bear#Verb|bear]].
#: {{ux|en|Paying the mortgage every month is a '''millstone''' round their necks.}}

